---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <!-- SEO Title & Description -->
    <title>24/7 Emergency Water Damage Restoration | SnappyX</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Flooded basement? Burst pipes? We provide 24/7 emergency water extraction, mold remediation, and drying services. We bill your insurance directly. Call Now." />
    
    <style>
      /* Simple & Fast CSS */
      body { font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      
      /* Header / Hero Section */
      .hero { 
        background: #004d99; /* Water Blue Color */
        color: white; 
        padding: 4rem 1rem; 
        text-align: center; 
      }
      .hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 800; }
      .hero p { font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
      
      /* Urgent Call Button */
      .call-btn { 
        background: #d32f2f; /* Urgent Red */
        color: white; 
        padding: 18px 35px; 
        font-size: 1.5rem; 
        text-decoration: none; 
        border-radius: 8px; 
        font-weight: bold; 
        display: inline-block;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        animation: pulse 2s infinite;
      }
      
      /* Services Grid */
      .features { padding: 3rem 1rem; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
      .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
      .card { border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; background: #f9f9f9; text-align: center; }
      .card h3 { color: #004d99; }

      /* Trust Section */
      .trust { background: #e6f7ff; padding: 2rem 1rem; text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; }

      @keyframes pulse {
        0% { transform: scale(1); }
        50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
        100% { transform: scale(1); }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>

    <!-- HERO SECTION (Pehle ye dikhega) -->
    <div class="hero">
      <h1>FLOODED BASEMENT?</h1>
      <p>We arrive in <strong>60 Minutes or Less</strong>. 24/7 Emergency Service.</p>
      
      <!-- Yahan apna Number dalna -->
      <a href="tel:555-0123" class="call-btn">üìû Call Now: (555) 012-3456</a>
      
      <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9rem;">üî¥ Live Technicians Available Right Now</p>
    </div>

    <!-- SERVICES SECTION -->
    <div class="features">
      <h2 style="text-align: center;">Our Emergency Services</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        
        <div class="card">
          <h3>üíß Water Extraction</h3>
          <p>Powerful pumps to remove standing water from basements and carpets immediately.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>‚ùÑÔ∏è Frozen/Burst Pipes</h3>
          <p>We fix the leak and dry the damage caused by winter pipe bursts.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>ü§¢ Sewage Cleanup</h3>
          <p>Safe removal of hazardous sewage backup. We sanitize and deodorize your home.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>üçÑ Mold Remediation</h3>
          <p>Prevent toxic mold growth with our industrial drying and dehumidification process.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- TRUST SECTION -->
    <div class="trust">
      <h2>Why Homeowners Trust Us?</h2>
      <p>‚úÖ <strong>$0 Out of Pocket:</strong> We bill your Insurance Company directly.</p>
      <p>‚úÖ <strong>Licensed & Insured:</strong> Fully certified IICRC technicians.</p>
      <p>‚úÖ <strong>30-60 Min Response:</strong> Because water damage gets worse every minute.</p>
    </div>

    <footer style="text-align: center; padding: 20px; background: #333; color: white;">
      <p>&copy; 2025 SnappyX Restoration Services</p>
    </footer>

  </body>
</html>
